Package: shinylabel
Title: R-Native Image Annotation Tool for YOLO Object Detection
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: person("Lalit", "BC", email = "lalitiaas@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A Shiny-based image annotation tool providing bounding box drawing,
    multi-annotator team support, SQLite-backed storage, and direct YOLO/COCO export.
    Supports standard RGB imagery as well as multispectral and hyperspectral TIFF
    files common in drone-based remote sensing workflows. Designed as a fully
    R-native alternative to LabelImg for YOLO-based object detection workflows.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
